<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Exclusive Offer Just for You!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .offer {
            background-color: #e8f0fe;
            border-left: 4px solid #007BFF;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888888;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Exclusive Offer Just for You!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= recipientName %>,</p>
            <p>Weâ€™re excited to offer you an exclusive discount on our latest products. Don't miss out on this special offer:</p>

            <div class="offer">
                <h2>Special Discount: <%= discount %></h2>
                <p><%= offerDetails %></p>
                <a href="<%= offerLink %>" class="button">Shop Now</a>
            </div>

            <p>This offer is only available for a limited time, so act fast!</p>
            <p>Thank you for being a valued customer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>If you no longer wish to receive these emails, you can <a href="<%= unsubscribeLink %>">unsubscribe here</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>